{"tid":2417417,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"這才是我認識的美國","createTime":"2021-02-22T00:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T02:46:41.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7ce0768f5a670b89532d25f0238c157d6b73dc","tid":2417417,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:51:10.000Z","msg":"這才是我認識的美國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=107027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D107027&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYzHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=f2984dbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=107027</a><br />\n<br />\n北極寒流侵襲美洲大陸，原本冬天溫度適中的德州，連續幾天暴風雪。冰雪封閉許多道路，居民進出不得。整個德州還有三百五十萬戶人家停電。<br />\n <br />\n艱難的環境也是發揮人性關懷的時刻。今天媒體有兩則新聞，都讓我看到原本認識的美國社會。<br />\n <br />\n第一則是華盛頓郵報點閱率最高的新聞，內容有關德州奧斯汀的一家超市。故事取材自一篇臉書貼文。<br />\n <br />\n在暴風雪侵襲德州後，這位臉書用戶外出採購，超市內人潮沸騰。突然停電了，所有收銀機停擺，信用卡不能使用，但多數顧客身上沒有現金。<br />\n <br />\n排隊付帳的顧客不知所措，但店員只揮手要他們往出口移動，沒人要他們把商品放回貨架。這位臉書用戶含著眼淚走出這家超級市場。<br />\n <br />\n停車場滿地泥濘，有人滑倒、有人物品掉落。深受超市義行感動的顧客，互相幫忙把物品裝上車。一位老太太的車子打滑，在場的幾位男士幫她把車子推上路。<br />\n <br />\n這篇臉書貼文在美國瘋傳，引起華盛頓郵報的注意。記者打電話要求採訪時，這家超市只證實有這件事，但拒絕接受採訪。真的是為善不欲人知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/content/20210221/XZ210221174850633166.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fcontent%2F20210221%2FXZ210221174850633166.jpg&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYzHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=37189870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/content/20210221/XZ210221174850633166.jpg</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y5Ad16u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5Ad16u.jpg&h=7eb0776e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二則是CNN的新聞，也發生在德州的奧斯汀。一位女送貨員的車子打滑，撞進一戶住家前院的花圃。主人出來查看駕駛是否需要幫忙，但發現車子卡住了。<br />\n <br />\n送貨員打電話請拖吊車援救，但路況實在太糟，拖吊車無法出門。住戶邀請送貨員進屋等候。她帶著口罩，在住戶的廚房不安的等候，誰知道這一等就是五天。<br />\n <br />\n這家住戶是對夫妻；送貨員是位年輕黑人女子。這對夫婦讓送貨員住進客房，還提供三餐。在這五天內，送貨員多次要去住旅館，但主人不讓她離開，因為旅館沒有提供食物。<br />\n <br />\n他們就像家人一樣，一起生活了五天。這對夫婦還做了情人節大餐招待送貨員；送貨員也烤了椰子蛋糕給這對夫婦品嚐。主人家的兩隻小狗，也和送貨員成為好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20210222072829704088.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20210222072829704088.jpg&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYzHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=d2c98955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20210222072829704088.jpg</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FSv4j1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FSv4j1.jpg&h=f1162b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n我好喜歡這樣的溫馨小故事。當事人都是一般的市井小民，在困難的時刻互相幫助，把人性最光明的一面激發出來。這不就是我認識的美國嗎！"},{"pid":"f518a9b553eb28894b77743b7b5b618029e68d87","tid":2417417,"uid":50386,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"德州先係咁<br />\n如果係加州<br />\n超市唔使免費都已經比人搶晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fde110cf92438e20e1c28b82b55018bc768853","tid":2417417,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f518a9b553eb28894b77743b7b5b618029e68d87","tid":2417417,"uid":50386,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"德州先係咁<br />\n如果係加州<br />\n超市唔使免費都已經比人搶晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:58:27.000Z","msg":"BLM!<br />\n唔俾人拎野走係歧視係謀殺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e78347cd82857fb17d5dc47220d9698f64fbe6","tid":2417417,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:24:24.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d423b51f57c9ce1643ae02f4edc2f30d8a618c","tid":2417417,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn0.wideopencountry.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Texas-793x525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.wideopencountry.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FTexas-793x525.jpg&h=610ee092&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af6a90518800043aa76653e4ac8419a6b1977bce","tid":2417417,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66d130468115b4311a53c1395f494f4c1f55d3b","tid":2417417,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"其實Austin係民主黨票倉<br />\n好多加州撚移居Austin<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}